## Report Features

Every report includes:

- **Executive Summary** - High-level overview of key findings
- **Key Performance Indicators** - Main metrics with averages and trends
- **Detailed Analysis** - Top performers and detailed insights
- **Data Quality Assessment** - Missing values and completeness check
- **Trends & Patterns** - Identified patterns and temporal trends
- **Recommendations** - Actionable next steps with priorities
- **Professional Formatting** - Clean, executive-ready layout

---

## Data Requirements

### Supported Formats
- **CSV** (.csv) - Comma-separated values
- **Excel** (.xlsx, .xls) - Microsoft Excel workbooks

### File Requirements
- Must contain headers (column names in first row)
- At least 1 row of data
- File size recommended under 10MB
- Columns should be clearly named

### Example Data Structure
```
Name,Department,Performance_Score,Attendance
Alice Sharma,Finance,92,98
Bob Kumar,HR,87,95
Charlie Patel,Tech,94,97
```

---

## How It Works

### 1. Upload Data
- Drag-and-drop or click to browse
- Supports CSV and Excel files
- File is analyzed instantly

### 2. System Detects
- Analyzes column names and data types
- Matches against 24 professional templates
- Shows detected template with confidence

### 3. You Configure
- Enter report title
- Select report type (or accept auto-detection)
- Choose advanced options (optional)

### 4. Generate Report
- System processes data
- Calculates statistics
- Creates professional narrative
- Usually takes 1-5 seconds

### 5. Review & Export
- Preview report in browser
- Export as PDF or TXT
- Download to your computer

