## Getting Started Guide

### Step 1: Prepare Your Data
```
‚úì Use CSV or Excel format
‚úì Include clear column headers
‚úì Ensure data is clean
‚úì Remove duplicate rows
‚úì Check date formats
```

### Step 2: Download & Extract
```
1. Download all 3 files: index.html, styles.css, script.js
2. Place in same folder
3. Keep folder name simple (e.g., "report-gen")
```

### Step 3: Open Application
```
Option A: Double-click index.html
Option B: Drag index.html into browser
Option C: Right-click ‚Üí Open with ‚Üí Browser
```

### Step 4: Generate Report
```
1. Click upload area
2. Select your data file
3. Enter report title
4. Click "Generate Report"
5. Review & export
```

